<!DOCTYPE html>
%html
  %head
    %meta{content: "text/html; charset=UTF-8", "http-equiv" => "Content-Type"}
  %body
    .indented.text-center
      %h2= "Hey #{@user.get_name_or_email.capitalize},"

      .text-left
        %span= "We have got more than #{Adventure.approved.count}" 
        %a{href: "#{root_url}/adventures"} adventures
        all over the world. So what will you do this winter to get out and adventure?

        %br
        %br
        .divider.divider-border

        %h3.text-center Here are a few of our favorites.
        %table#main{border: "0", cellpadding: "0", cellspacing: "20", width: "100%"}
          %tr
            %td
              - adventure = Adventure.find(154)
              %a{href: "#{root_url}adventures/#{adventure.slug}", style: 'text-decoration: none; color: #000;'}
                %img{alt: adventure.title, height: "100px", src: adventure.attachment.url(:medium), width: "auto", style: 'margin-left: -25px; margin-right: 10px;'}
                .text-left{style: 'word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 12px; width: 120px; margin-left: -25px;'}= adventure.title
                %strong{style: 'margin-left: -25px;'}= adventure.location
            %td
              - adventure = Adventure.find(119)
              %a{href: "#{root_url}adventures/#{adventure.slug}", style: 'text-decoration: none; color: #000;'}
                %img{alt: adventure.title, height: "100px", src: adventure.attachment.url(:medium), width: "auto", style: 'margin-left: -25px; margin-right: 10px;'}
                .text-left{style: 'word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 12px; width: 120px; margin-left: -25px;'}= adventure.title
                %strong{style: 'margin-left: -25px;'}= adventure.location
            %td
              - adventure = Adventure.find(127)
              %a{href: "#{root_url}adventures/#{adventure.slug}", style: 'text-decoration: none; color: #000;'}
                %img{alt: adventure.title, height: "100px", src: adventure.attachment.url(:medium), width: "auto", style: 'margin-left: -25px; margin-right: 10px;'}
                .text-left{style: 'word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 12px; width: 120px; margin-left: -25px;'}= adventure.title
                %strong{style: 'margin-left: -25px;'}= "#{adventure.city}, #{adventure.state}".capitalize


        .divider.divider-border
        %br
        %br

      %i Safe travels,
      %br
      %a{href: "#{root_url}about"} The Advlo Team